    <section id="id6154751">
      <title>AFRICAN DANCE</title>
      <para id="id1571881">DANCE</para>
      <para id="id6522591">This term you will be exploring the exciting genre of ‘African Dance’ and you will create your own African Dance for Heritage Day in September!</para>
      <para id="id8904489">First you need to warm up your body in order for you to use your body to its full capacity.</para>
    </section>
